{"tid":1916567,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼城又有新轉會目標 砸8550萬鎊搶國米後衛","createTime":"2020-03-09T03:03:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T03:22:50.000Z","uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"de933311e6732645841b1e8fe38f65dd64c7e991","tid":1916567,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:03:01.000Z","msg":"意大利傳媒報道，曼城準備在轉會市場，出手簽入現年24歲的國際米蘭後衛史堅尼亞（Milan Skriniar），據指曼城準備出價8550萬英鎊，為球隊後防增強。早前，曼城亦據報有意簽入馬體會中場沙奧尼古斯。<br />\n<br />\n現年32歲的高柏尼（Vincent Kompany）仍沒有和曼城簽下新一張的合約，至於31歲的奧達文迪（ Nicol&aacute;s Otamendi）今季很難取得穩定正選位置。 據報道，去年曼城和曼聯都有傳希望簽下史堅尼亞，而球員的經理人表示曼城的報價遭到了拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n曼城目前的收購標王是迪布尼，2015年夏天，「藍月亮」支付6840萬鎊從禾夫斯堡簽下了這位比利時國腳。如果想簽下史堅尼亞，曼城必定會打破球會的收購紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/BBVbgqq.img?h=450&amp;w=799&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f&amp;x=529&amp;y=86\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FBBVbgqq.img%3Fh%3D450%26w%3D799%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df%26x%3D529%26y%3D86&h=4294d6b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44e031c79c0899fe3d0c91fd03118afdebd97d80","tid":1916567,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bcfa0016bb3903537301ce89d81393764e10387","tid":1916567,"uid":50041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:04:31.000Z","msg":"現年32歲的高柏尼（Vincent Kompany）仍沒有和曼城簽下新一張的合約"},{"pid":"85ee286ad248c5ecb99c8f9720ef77d097e89cf5","tid":1916567,"uid":199804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bcfa0016bb3903537301ce89d81393764e10387","tid":1916567,"uid":50041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:04:31.000Z","msg":"現年32歲的高柏尼（Vincent Kompany）仍沒有和曼城簽下新一張的合約"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T03:06:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i